# Database
*.db
*.sqlite3
*.sql
# ...but the app-schema DDL run by setup_db.py MUST be tracked (this is what
# creates the DQ_APP tables on a fresh clone — the reason harsh's branch
# couldn't boot was these files being ignored).
!backend/snowflake/*.sql
# Never commit the throwaway GET_DDL dump helper output.
backend/snowflake/_*.sql

